rows.label: qst702302_msg0003
rows.name:
...He's there.
Enough hiding. Come out and face us.

rows.label: qst702302_msg0005
rows.name: What are you doing here, man?

rows.label: qst702302_msg0006
rows.name:
Apologies, Ma'am.
I got turned around.
First time in Iira, y'see.

rows.label: qst702302_msg0007
rows.name:
A lost Superbian soldier...?
Now where have I heard that before?

rows.label: qst702302_msg0008
rows.name:
Ah, could you be Meknes,
from Iris's unit...?

rows.label: qst702302_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh yeah, that was it! Iris-san's really
worried about you, you know...

rows.label: qst702302_msg0012
rows.name: Looks like there's no fooling you...

rows.label: qst702302_msg0013
rows.name:
Nothing for it. I can make my escape
over your dead bodies...
